# Informal Signage: Venting Hazard

**Location / Context:** Maintenance shafts in sector 7G, warning locals of real dangers the official signs ignore or fail to communicate properly.
**Visual Description:** A sketched skull-and-crossbones wearing a broken space helmet.

**English Text:**
> __entry#NEG#CL9 beyond#LOC bulkhead.#DEM#CL9 hazard#CL9 venting.#POSS Unless want#2SG kiss#INF void.#CL9__
"No entry beyond this bulkhead. Venting hazard. Unless you want to kiss the void."
